<li> A Killing Rune which compels those who view it to draw it themselves before death, thus spreading its contagion to others.
</ul>

<br class="page-break">
All of which are believed to have entered our world through the Information Anomaly.

Whether due to neglect or malice, the inhabitants of Universe SCP are responsible for the deaths of over one hundred of our people: in some cases, souls thousands of years old have been lost forever. All attempts to sever the Information Anomaly linkage between our universes have failed. 

The only recourse left to us is the destruction of Universe SCP and the deaths of all inhabitants therein.

Esoterica classification has been updated from Exploratory to Strategic. Former Project Manager I__ C__ is removed from the project and is to have no further contact with Esoterica.

Project Manager: Grand Unifier M__
Project Priority: Existential.

